(@p4, @p5);
DECLARE @inserted3 TABLE ([Id] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Colors] USING (
VALUES (@p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, 1),
(@p10, @p11, 2),
(@p12, @p13, 3)) AS i ([Code], [Name], _Position) ON 1=0

VALUES (i.[Code], i.[Name])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted3;

INNER JOIN @inserted3 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
